<title>  Tian's Homepage </title>

<h1>Xiao Tian's Homepage</h1>
<!WA0><img src="http://www.cs.bgsu.edu/~xtian/me.gif">
This page links to various sources of information on the internet,
related to China, or written in the Chinese language. 
 To view Chinese using mosaic, you need a 
<!WA1><a href = "http://www.ntt.jp/Mosaic-l10n">  Multi-lingual version of 
mosaic</a>,  a copy of which can be found at the software archive at <!WA2><a 
href = "ftp://ifcss.org/software/x-win/www"> ifcss.org</a>.
<p>
<!WA3><img src="http://www.cs.bgsu.edu/~xtian/green_bar.gif">
<p>
<!WA4><img src = "http://www.cs.bgsu.edu/~xtian/ball.gif">
<!WA5><a href ="http://www.cnd.org"> China News Digest (HXWZ)</a>
maintains one of the best servers for Chinese information in North
America.
<p>
<h2> This is ABC_Buying Group </h2>
